revision.text:
{{Documentation subpage}}
{{High-use}}
This template generates an icon for the specified image given in {{para|1}}, matching the size, [[CSS]] class, and other attributes of images produced by {{tl|Flag icon}}. It can be used for arbitrary images not included in any [[:Category:Country data templates]].

Please consider the [[Wikipedia:Manual of Style (icons)#Flags|Manual of Style section on flags]] before using this template. Use caution when applying this template in infoboxes, as flags are generally discouraged in that context per [[MOS:INFOBOXFLAG]]. Additional considerations include avoiding flags used purely for decoration and ensuring historical accuracy. For further guidance, see [[MOS:FLAGS]].

{{resbox|[[File:Red copyright.svg|18x18px|link=]] ''Do not use this template to display [[Wikipedia:Non-free images|non-free images]], as they are also not permitted in country data templates.''}}

;Usage
: <code><nowiki>{{flagicon image|image name|size=optional|border=optional|link=optional}}</nowiki></code>
;Examples
: <code><nowiki>{{flagicon image|Red flag.svg}}</nowiki></code> → {{flagicon image|Red flag.svg}}
: <code><nowiki>{{flagicon image|Red flag.svg|size=30x20px|link=Japan}}</nowiki></code> → {{flagicon image|Red flag.svg|size=30x20px|link=Japan}}
: <code><nowiki>{{flagicon image|ICS Alfa.svg|border=}}</nowiki></code> → {{flagicon image|ICS Alfa.svg|border=}}

== See also ==
{{tl|ListFlag}}

<includeonly>{{Sandbox other||
[[Category:Flag template system| ]]

}}</includeonly>

